name: CryptoApes
description:
CryptoApes is the flagship character of Primary Alt- a modern studio focused on creating alternative identities and experiences through innovative NFT-based utilities and storytelling.

Hold at least one CryptoApes for access to unique experiences (treasure hunts), innovative upcoming utility (ability to temporarily transfer utility of any NFT), web3 education-focused Discord community, IRL events, and priority access to Primary Alt's marketplaces and ecosystem.
